Mother Russia Bleeds is an ultra-violent co-op brawler overflowing
with an unmistakable style and unforgettably brutal action for up
to four players at once. Set in an alternate U.S.S.R, the story
centers on a desperate crew of imprisoned street fighters that must
overcome an oppressive criminal authority and forced drug
addictions through any means necessary
